13:44.067 --> 13:47.497
<b>My name is Shiina. I'm a lieutenant
 with the Kanagawa prefectural police.</b>

13:47.497 --> 13:49.227
<b>Furuna, Second Anti-Devil Division.</b>

13:49.687 --> 13:52.737
<b>I'm Kishibe, commander of the Fourth Special Division.</b>

13:53.237 --> 13:58.077
<b>Today, the police and Second Division are sealing the exits from the basement and the first floor,</b>

13:58.077 --> 14:01.747
<b>while the Fourth Special Division
 will be dealing with the terrorists inside.</b>

14:02.287 --> 14:06.747
<b>Thus, there is only one thing
 for you to be paying attention to.</b>

14:07.037 --> 14:11.507
<b>Most members of the Fourth Special Division
 are non-humans.</b>

14:11.817 --> 14:13.957
<b>If anyone from the Fourth escapes into the city,</b>

14:13.957 --> 14:17.507
<b>they'll cause more harm
 than these terrorists ever could.</b>

14:18.157 --> 14:23.967
<b>So you need to be prepared for battle
 with the Fourth rather than with terrorists.</b>

14:23.967 --> 14:26.387
<b>I'll explain how to deal with each member.</b>

14:26.897 --> 14:29.017
<b>Zombie! Zombie!</b>

14:32.027 --> 14:35.277
<b>It's all-I-can-eat!</b>

14:39.687 --> 14:41.177
<b>The Shark Fiend.{BEAM THE GOAT}</b>

14:41.177 --> 14:44.537
<b>He can swim through all kinds of surfaces,
 like walls and the ground.</b>

14:45.337 --> 14:48.207
<b>For short periods of time,
 he can regain his devil form.</b>

14:57.077 --> 14:58.887
<b>Oh, sorry about that.</b>

14:59.577 --> 15:01.757
<b>You looked so bite-y, I mistook you for a zombie.</b>

15:04.947 --> 15:06.707
<b>The Violence Fiend.</b>

15:06.707 --> 15:10.507
<b>Normally, a devil gets weaker
 when it becomes a fiend.</b>

15:10.507 --> 15:15.147
<b>But this one's too strong even as a fiend,
 so we have him wear a poison-filled mask at all times.</b>

15:15.537 --> 15:18.077
<b>Whatever happens, don't remove his mask.</b>

15:19.237 --> 15:22.567
<b>Hey, girl, you should get out of here.</b>

15:22.567 --> 15:25.407
<b>If a human gets bitten, they turn into a zombie.</b>

15:27.687 --> 15:29.707
<b>Oh, you're a devil.</b>

15:33.297 --> 15:35.117
<b>The Spider Devil.{hey it's that spider girl anime but older}</b>

15:35.117 --> 15:37.797
<b>Most of the time, she maintains a human form.</b>

15:38.357 --> 15:43.297
<b>Devils that appear human are usually
 friendly towards us, but a devil is still a devil.</b>

15:44.287 --> 15:45.927
<b>She'll kill humans if they bother her.</b>

15:51.377 --> 15:52.647
<b>Yuck.</b>

15:52.647 --> 15:54.967
<b>Now my shoes are filthy.</b>

15:54.967 --> 15:56.567
<b>This is the worst.</b>

16:02.217 --> 16:03.657
<b>The Angel Devil.</b>

16:04.037 --> 16:08.157
<b>He's a special case, and has no animosity
 towards humans, but don't get near him.</b>

16:08.537 --> 16:11.197
<b>Touching him drains your lifespan.</b>

16:22.707 --> 16:23.887
<b>Hey, you.</b>

16:24.217 --> 16:25.767
<b>Got a handkerchief?</b>

16:37.527 --> 16:40.217
<b>I'm surprised how willing you are to get close to me.</b>

16:40.217 --> 16:42.777
<b>Touching me would shorten your lifespan.</b>

16:43.297 --> 16:45.287
<b>Through cloth is fine, if I recall correctly.</b>

16:47.677 --> 16:48.657
<b>Ouch.</b>

16:53.507 --> 16:56.127
<b>Devil, take this man outside.</b>

16:58.727 --> 17:01.507
<b>It's better than fighting, at least.</b>

17:01.507 --> 17:02.217
<b>You three.</b>

17:02.217 --> 17:03.387
<b>Huh?{each of the three}</b>

17:03.387 --> 17:05.747
<b>The fiends can handle this.</b>

17:05.747 --> 17:08.417
<b>We're going for the samurai-sword man
 and the snake woman.</b>

17:08.417 --> 17:11.107
<b>What? You know where to look?</b>

17:11.107 --> 17:11.847
<b>No.</b>

17:12.367 --> 17:13.727
<b>Split up and look for them.</b>

19:08.387 --> 19:10.387
<b>Give yourself up and—</b>

19:09.347 --> 19:10.387
<b>Snake.{timing: overlaps with the above a bit?}</b>

19:10.887 --> 19:11.967
<b>Spit out.</b>

19:23.577 --> 19:25.357
<b>Damn you!</b>

19:30.437 --> 19:31.237
<b>Ghost.</b>

19:31.837 --> 19:33.097
<b>Kill that man.</b>

19:49.287 --> 19:51.297
<b>You're fighting better than last time.</b>

19:51.297 --> 19:56.677
<b>With my power, your right eye
 can see a little while into the future.{Clairvoyance C+}</b>

20:15.067 --> 20:17.117
<b>Up to you to use what you see, though.{TLC: mmm this works well and flows good but is somewhat bordering on a mistranslation. He's literally saying: "But that's all you can do" or "That's all my power does, though"}{assuming this is fine}</b>

20:36.927 --> 20:38.767
<b>Go ahead and strangle him to death.</b>

20:38.767 --> 20:41.767
<b></b>

